snippet.title: Heretic - The Curse of D'sparil
snippet.description:
Map01 demo vid of my mod The Curse of D'sparil for Heretic.
The video is recorded playing in Zdoom. But it will work in anything supporting Heretic and got limits removed.

EDIT: This has been released. Go get it at: http://www.doomworld.com/vb/post/844750
